videos.description: Virginia's Casey Morsell drives, spins around a defender and gets his runner to drop while drawing a foul.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Morsell sinks spinning and-1 bucket for Virginia) 2020/01/28

videos.headline: Morsell sinks spinning and-1 bucket for Virginia

videos.description: Virginia's Jay Huff dishes to Braxton Key, who aggressively drives to the rim for the two-handed slam.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Key glides to the rim for the jam) 2020/01/28

videos.headline: Key glides to the rim for the jam

videos.description: After being called for an offensive foul, Virginia's Braxton Key rips his jersey and is forced to wear a new one.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Virginia player rips jersey in frustration) 2020/01/28

videos.headline: Virginia player rips jersey in frustration

videos.description: Malik Osborne is rejected at the rim, but grabs the rebound and somehow gets his second effort to fall despite being surrounded by Virginia defenders.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (FSU's Osborne hits circus and-1 layup) 2020/01/28

videos.headline: FSU's Osborne hits circus and-1 layup
